{"tid":2000894,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"馮盈盈戴祖儀亂入花叢堆影相 頭痛頭暈作嘔疑中毒","createTime":"2020-05-04T07:07:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-04T09:11:07.000Z","uid":137088,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"b41a29bdf1eae6436f856caf386d8422b0346bdf","tid":2000894,"uid":137088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T07:07:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ldy/20200503/s00009/8cdbc735e9c403aea5c69597787c1271.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fldy%2F20200503%2Fs00009%2F8cdbc735e9c403aea5c69597787c1271.jpg&h=ee1d65df&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n戴祖儀（左）與馮盈盈胡亂走入路邊的花叢中影相，結果疑中毒，頭痛頭暈又作嘔。（戴祖儀、馮盈盈Instagram圖片 / 明報製圖）<br />\n<br />\n戴祖儀（Joey）今日在Instagram上載身處粉紅花叢中的照片，開心表示在香港找到櫻花，又笑言︰「只要有童心，櫻花都變成真。」誰知她後來補充︰「喊出嚟，原來依（呢）種花叫夾竹桃，係有毒的～大家千祈唔好學我哋去影。」馮盈盈留言致歉︰「對唔住，係我發現棵花先，係我差啲害咗你。」<br />\n<br />\n馮盈盈之後在其Instagram出post說︰「昨日幫戴祖儀係（喺）路邊嘅花叢中影相留倩影，心諗行街途中都見到如斯嬌美嘅花，世界真美好，但番（返）到屋企到今朝，又頭痛又作嘔，唔知點解，直至Joey問我︰『你有無頭暈作悶嘅徵狀？』原來，那棵粉紅色的花樹，係有劇毒的夾竹桃。故事教訓：路邊的野花不要採，也不要亂接觸，只遠觀好喇。#差點因為影相而中毒的兩位少女，#無啦啦變咗生死之交 #為藝術豁出去 #大家千萬唔好學」<br />\n<br />\n馮盈盈回覆《明報》記者查詢時表示︰「我依家無事喇，多謝關心。應該要食先中毒，所以我應該好輕微。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ol.mingpao.com/ldy/showbiz/latest/20200503/1588515259204/%e9%a6%ae%e7%9b%88%e7%9b%88%e6%88%b4%e7%a5%96%e5%84%80%e4%ba%82%e5%85%a5%e8%8a%b1%e5%8f%a2%e5%a0%86%e5%bd%b1%e7%9b%b8-%e9%a0%ad%e7%97%9b%e9%a0%ad%e6%9a%88%e4%bd%9c%e5%98%94%e7%96%91%e4%b8%ad%e6%af%92\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fol.mingpao.com%2Fldy%2Fshowbiz%2Flatest%2F20200503%2F1588515259204%2F%25e9%25a6%25ae%25e7%259b%2588%25e7%259b%2588%25e6%2588%25b4%25e7%25a5%2596%25e5%2584%2580%25e4%25ba%2582%25e5%2585%25a5%25e8%258a%25b1%25e5%258f%25a2%25e5%25a0%2586%25e5%25bd%25b1%25e7%259b%25b8-%25e9%25a0%25ad%25e7%2597%259b%25e9%25a0%25ad%25e6%259a%2588%25e4%25bd%259c%25e5%2598%2594%25e7%2596%2591%25e4%25b8%25ad%25e6%25af%2592&d=LQBsT8b49a%2FdXTDbQfnWX2CvuqnjOb%2FiGpmC2gL%2Fng4%3D&h=cdeab076\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fol.mingpao.com%2Fldy%2Fshowbiz%2Flatest%2F20200503%2F1588515259204%2F%25e9%25a6%25ae%25e7%259b%2588%25e7%259b%2588%25e6%2588%25b4%25e7%25a5%2596%25e5%2584%2580%25e4%25ba%2582%25e5%2585%25a5%25e8%258a%25b1%25e5%258f%25a2%25e5%25a0%2586%25e5%25bd%25b1%25e7%259b%25b8-%25e9%25a0%25ad%25e7%2597%259b%25e9%25a0%25ad%25e6%259a%2588%25e4%25bd%259c%25e5%2598%2594%25e7%2596%2591%25e4%25b8%25ad%25e6%25af%2592&h=78c80543\" target=\"_blank\">https://ol.mingpao.com/ldy/showbiz/latest/20200503/1588515259204/%e9%a6%ae%e7%9b%88%e7%9b%88%e6%88%b4%e7%a5%96%e5%84%80%e4%ba%82%e5%85%a5%e8%8a%b1%e5%8f%a2%e5%a0%86%e5%bd%b1%e7%9b%b8-%e9%a0%ad%e7%97%9b%e9%a0%ad%e6%9a%88%e4%bd%9c%e5%98%94%e7%96%91%e4%b8%ad%e6%af%92</a>"},{"pid":"4a7202cb5b10ec9d43efe08eab227767f51e59a8","tid":2000894,"uid":122134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T07:09:30.000Z","msg":"fyy張相想點..."},{"pid":"605fafd7525827f50721e187c0645ca7f4bd2759","tid":2000894,"uid":68689,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T07:10:06.000Z","msg":"食先中毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />佢食左呀?"},{"pid":"1b1aac659cceaa3d5b8d8bcb96d75c02221c220a","tid":2000894,"uid":25659,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T07:10:47.000Z","msg":"成件事已經好7<br />\n加埋fyy最後嗰句真係7上加7<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1f3ad5272d7283aee6983d18f94b028472b3ee5","tid":2000894,"uid":268519,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T07:15:55.000Z","msg":"#為藝術豁出去  藝術？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08080f7f3674e86be88d483d7955763d5477176e","tid":2000894,"uid":70685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T07:18:49.000Z","msg":"cctvb關香港人撚事 返大陸搵生意啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cefb0c3cac89b4d80ac7b4ce889adb654042a9c7","tid":2000894,"uid":55960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"